                <h1>Fuqua bucks trend, sees increases in business school applications</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/5d7b1b6c-21e1-40e1-ac5b-014ebc1f5490.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            

